Giving a Complete Alphabetical List of Business Firms and Private Citizens of the City of Vallejo, and the Name, Occupation and Post Office Address of Adult Residents of the County; Also a Classified Business Directory of the County.

 Vallejo, California: A. Kingsbury, Press of Vallejo Chronicle, 1904.

 This directory for Vallejo includes a brief city history that mentions the 1898 Mare Island earthquake.  It also contains a short sketch of Solano County by Rev. Theo. F. Burnham, M.A.

 Octavo: [2], 218, [4] pp. including the endpapers and boards, which feature numerous advertisements, plus two color inserts. Original green cloth binding, with stamping in black.

 The catalog record is available [here](https://search.library.ucdavis.edu/permalink/01UCD_INST/9fle3i/alma991001652863303126).
